name: Predator Cybercats - Link
description: Link the Lynx. Shifty, trickster, and will outsmart the best of them. The ultimate survivalist and master at adapting to situations. What he doesn't possess in brawn he makes up for by always being one step ahead of those that challenge him. Ability to phase through solid matter and create illusions. Wears out his prey and finishes them off with toxic fangs.Gang leader in the frozen planet of Exodus.
